=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你睇片就知白偉俊有幾咁on9 講埋啲師奶嘢 又抽才子廁紙包頭 講第一次才子都忍住 因為諗住講正經嘢 費事彩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />後尾又再講才子先笑鳩佢同白姐姐 後尾知衰7到唔講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毓民 才子 劉大狀講緊深層次嘅嘢 佢同甘先生仲講緊扔磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc18fd357712091ab3e8d3110fdf85e7b0876c18","tid":1980722,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:57:14.000Z","msg":"講紙巾包頭才子爆SEED!!!!"},{"pid":"25a45db56a8c17c94389cb165be902d120eb5d1c","tid":1980722,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:57:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借個位先 召喚聯署師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=f2a853ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A部分請㩒入去呢度<br />\n記得睇埋啊，好撚緊要啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">【偽 &middot; 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版<br />\n召喚聯署師長文Q&amp;A就放喺度啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981260</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"4065f61a793c82f984ca284259055a9e50fa5994","tid":1980722,"uid":34222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"謝偉俊同甘文鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個奶白姐姐 一個奶葉劉<br />\n<br />\n諗起都重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}